Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not eating this, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.06,0:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Geez! But I love it—\NI was saving it for last!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.32,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.36,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again, would you?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what again?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hadn't you eaten your seaweed yet?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.81,0:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.93,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love it?
Comment: 2,0:00:31.40,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.65,0:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've memorized the way you looked\Nand sounded when you said "love" to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look, it's the {\i1}seaweed{\i0} I love, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... a guy can dream, can't he?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go. We're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.90,0:00:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\i0} like seaweed, but what I like even more...
Comment: 2,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleah!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb ol' Kanade...
Comment: 2,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This rain sure came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.15,0:02:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our shoulders are so close...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin's like marshmallows...\NI could eat it up.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I twisted my ankle.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho... hang on tight.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.81,0:03:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's heartbeat,\Nhis hot breath—they surround me.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? I want to stay like this forever!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That ought to do the trick.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.31,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Kanade.\NYou're good at this first-aid thing.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.81,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming for Tokyo University,\Nso I'm studying all kinds of stuff.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.48,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A rainbow! Look, Kanade—a rainbow!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.98,0:04:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? They say there's\Ntreasure buried at the end of the rainbow.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.85,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day we met,\Nthere's been a rainbow in my heart, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And my... my treasure...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want your sprain to get worse.\NRest here in the infirmary, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get my teacher's permission\Nto leave early and come get you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go home together.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're coming, too?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta have a hero to\Nkeep the treasure safe, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Never know when a bad guy's\Ngonna come by to steal it!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that!\NA bad guy—here, of all places.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no way to talk to your teacher, Kanade.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give you Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me. I'll just have to take her.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Kanade going to be okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, a skate-off against Mr. Taga...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives, Kazu?\NDon't you have any faith in Kanade?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.44,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taga's the legendary roller-skater\Nwho once took the world by storm:
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rollin' Atu-see!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Atu-see!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya mean... Taga's that Rollin' Atu-see guy?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Atu-see!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.01,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known as "Mr. Rolling Eternity"!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternity!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.35,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one feared as the\N"Pandora's Box on Wheels"?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,On wheels!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Canelé pastries came out of Taga's armpits!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And soft mochi rice cakes came out of Kanade's!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's mochi cakes\Nare engulfing Mr. Taga's canelé!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,White canelé? This is revolutionary!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This warmth, brimming with kindness...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's soft mochi {\i1}inside{\i0} the canelé, too?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Canelé with a soft mochi center?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.20,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this mean... Kanade was\Nalready inside Taga's soul?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chewy, crispy, chewy...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.66,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's heat is radiating through\NTaga's canelé both inside and out!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gettin' hot in here, all right!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth gone white...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.69,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sketching out love\Nacross this big campus of ours.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You win, Kanade.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho? I got that early-dismissal form stamped.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You may still be sleeping now...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.99,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if you ever start to love me\Nso much you can't live without me,
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.04,0:08:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,be sure you wake up, Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.37,0:08:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been like that for\Na long time now, Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awfully glum today, Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with Kanade?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the setting sun / Soft cheeks flushing\Nhotly pink / Here, then: here is love.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, Kouta, a haiku!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping the spirit of popular poet\NMatsuo Basho alive, I see!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho stimulates my haiku-heart.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That expression of hers was sublime!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A rather fine poem, too, if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayhap I'll submit it to the\Nhaiku column in am-am Magazine.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! It's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't—{\i1}if{\i0} you speak of\Nthe worry hidden in your heart.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's... too dazzling.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.21,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! You just had the\Nmost amazing look on your face.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.18,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaho—I've got an exhibition\Ncoming up in New York. Model for me?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't taken my showpiece photo yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.10,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the setting sun / Tinting the tears\Nthat now fall / Here, then: here is love.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, take a look at Chiaki, would you?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, a-are you going\Nto make Kaho your m-model?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.37,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to! Let {\i1}me{\i0}\Nbe the only one in your viewfinder!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally told me\Nhow you really feel, Chiaki.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.44,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on—my lens is always\Nfocused on you and you alone!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.48,0:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.65,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful! I want to be like them.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear—and me the\Nonly one unattached. How lonely.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're so popular with the girls, Kouta!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems romance doesn't\Nquite fit that 5-7-5 pattern.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a struggle, I tell you. I'll be\Npartnered with poetry for a while yet...
Comment: 2,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade? Um, I—
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. My manager's looking for me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.65,0:11:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade? Hey, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... manager?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaho. I've kept it\Nfrom you all this time, but I...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.88,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idol.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad runs a talent agency.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.83,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He first let me on the lot when\Nhe needed someone to play Passerby A,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but after that...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An idol?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.31,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls squeeing at events,\Nsqueeing at meet-and-greets,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,squeeing at magazine interviews,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,squeeing when he says "p-o-o-p"?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} kind of idol, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My... my heart hurts, somehow.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I thought he was mine alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, listen...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.40,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this preview event for the\Npremiere of this drama I'm starring in,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be reenacting key scenes as part of it.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to do a kiss scene.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How does your drama's kiss scene go?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kanade—don't kiss me there!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you prefer?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair! You're always\Nwinding me up like this...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in the infirmary today—
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you heard my confession?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.40,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So my secret's out.\NNow I don't know which way to turn.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lame.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not! You're cool, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Kanade, your ears are bright red!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what you're saying\Nmakes me want to jump for joy!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I've wanted\Nto say this for a while now:
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho, be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.23,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You shine so brightly,\Nand your words hold such happiness...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I smiled, looking like I was about to cry.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This love: it's adorable.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.92,Alt,,0,0,0,,Miss Nikaidou? Miss Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kaho-yan! Kaho-yan?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.36,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Am I...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey! You okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.06,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.39,Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on back!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck, Kanade?\NFightin' with Kaho-yan again?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.81,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting? That's right! I—
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...with you anymore...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was a dream? A daydream?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.98,0:13:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too close!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must go on a journey.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I might even marry Sadako someday.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadako's a dog. Can you even marry a dog?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade—it can't be!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadako bit me.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Kanade?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't good... no, sirree!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadako's a human-faced dog!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.38,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're bitten by a\Nhuman-faced dog, you turn into one.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.97,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a friend in Shiga whose relative's\Ncousin's uncle's coworker's son got bit,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and {\i1}he{\i0} turned into a human-faced dog!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a dog soon!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.51,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade! No, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They totally believe it!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Kanade:
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}not{\i0} a human-faced dog.\NIt's just a regular ugly dog.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Say {\i1}what{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.38,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I found out you were\Nsecretly looking after this ugly dog,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I took this ugly dog to the vet
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and got this ugly dog its shots.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So... so Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right: he won't turn into a\Nhuman-faced dog. He'll stay human.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray for Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better this way!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kaho?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can totally tell just by looking!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All this fuss 'cause you fell for an\Nurban legend hook, line, and sinker! Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How obnoxious can you get?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}always{\i0} like that, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.53,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always, always, always,\N{\i1}always{\i0} saying the weirdest things!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.74,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we met, you've set up\NI don't even {\i1}know{\i0} how many gags!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest thing about you is that body!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.60,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling myself it's a\Ngrowth spurt, but is it? Is it {\i1}really{\i0}?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! I don't care if you suddenly grow bigger—
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't just explain\Nit away as a growth spurt!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too darn sloppy!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I thought your backpack was a custom order,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but no, it's ready-made\Nand just {\i1}jammed{\i0} onto your back!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You wear that gym outfit {\i1}every single day{\i0}—
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,how many gym outfits do you {\i1}have{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And those {\i1}bangs{\i0}!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always in that M shape—
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't anyone tell you to cut\Nthem when they grow into your eyes?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For as much as you act the\Ngrade-schooler when it's convenient,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,why must you do the hunk thing\Nwhen it comes to your {\i1}bangs{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the "p**p" and "w**ner"\Nschtick and {\i1}cut your bangs{\i0}!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you end up missing\Nthe truth you've got to see!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first date was a stroll\Naround the neighborhood!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You pushed me down onto my bed,\Nbut then gave me a massage—
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and a {\i1}good{\i0} one, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all "P**p! W**ner! P**p! W**ner!"
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was glad {\i1}not{\i0} to\Nbe traded for a {\i1}Pachimon{\i0} card,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you suggest we all date together!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the "p**p" and "w**ner" talk!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.31,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You used a {\i1}hula-hoop{\i0}\Nto decide if we should break up?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.94,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,P**p!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You proposed to me on a {\i1}harmonica{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.01,0:16:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,P**p and w**ner, you saw me in my underwear
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with no p**pin' reaction!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,P**p! W**ner! P**p! W**ner! P**p! W**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.66,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny about p**p and w**ners, anyway?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.92,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,P**p! W**ner! P**p! W**ner! P**p! W**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a riot, Kaho!\NThat was a {\i1}ton{\i0} of poop and w**ners!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For all those crazy complaints\Nto come spilling out...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't come from the likes of—
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No saying "the likes of me." Remember?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, ending your sentences\Nwith "poop" and "w**ner" is super fun!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to you, Kaho! What a find!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That girlfriend of his is a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what grown-up women do for dirty jokes?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girl I fell for once upon a time:
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.85,0:18:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho-yan! No, Kaho-chin! No, Kaho-p**-p**!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.67,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho-p**-p**!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho-p**-p**!!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho-p**-p**!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho-p**-p**! Kaho-p**-p**!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, gang!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The afternoon events are about to begin.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and enjoy your sports festival, now.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will! Thanks, Atsushi!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat's ready, folks!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take some meat, w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too, w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good, w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crazy tasty, w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.08,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? What are you all saying?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a game they picked up from Kaho.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I didn't see {\i1}that{\i0} coming...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff... sniff...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.40,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of your lower half\Nis a feast unto itself, Shuugo.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.35,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mafuyu!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop—that kind of thing\Ncould get you in trouble!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Sadako, s*t up and b*g.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that dog is\Ncoming to stay at Kasumi House.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Taga worked\Nthings out with Mr. Takahashi.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From this distance,\NKanade looks like the ideal boyfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He does, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.06,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't just want to look at him from afar.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.15,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Kanade to be just this hot guy.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.10,0:20:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I'm out of meat.\NLet's get seconds, Arashi.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Chiaki.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaho...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade, that's great news about Sadako, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.44,0:20:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw Sadako abandoned like that,\NI thought she looked just like you.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like {\i1}you{\i0} were abandoned...\Nand I just couldn't leave her like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are we really that alike?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadako...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:12.44,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stay together forever!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cool, I feel this tightness in my chest.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes so little sense\Nsometimes, I'm just shocked.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's Kanade.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for meeting me, Kanade.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for making me your girlfriend, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.81,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho, Kaho!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.98,0:21:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.98,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster called\N"first love" is still coming after me.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can take any attack it dishes out.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.78,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I love Kanade\Njust the way he is—right now!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.82,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:04.73,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sadako's got a w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's a w**ner, all right.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.12,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No mistakin' that w**ner.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.08,0:22:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's a boy?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. The "ko" in "Sadako" is for "coj*nes."
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.85,0:22:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's ugly {\i1}and{\i0} a boy?!
Comment: 2,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.40,0:22:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our final meeting, so I'd like\Nto take this opportunity to say something.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.85,0:22:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of Kanade a trillion times more\Nthan that crappy dumb idiot girl does.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to caring about\NKanade, I simply can't be beat.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.26,0:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't get away with sayin' that around me!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that I was more seriously\Nworried for Kanade than you were
Dialogue: 2,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,during the human-faced-dog incident, Taga.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ah! It tickles when you lick me there!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.66,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught up in your grown-up common sense,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd made up your mind at the start\Nthat Sadako wasn't a human-faced dog.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.05,0:23:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I considered the possibility that he {\i1}was{\i0},
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and if Kanade became one himself,
Dialogue: 2,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was prepared to, too—right along with him!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Th-that's my {\i1}gyun{\i0} spot! Don't...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I{\i0} thought of that, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.98,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd{\i0} decided to dedicate the rest of my life
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to developing a drug that would turn him back!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.51,0:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all are thinkin' too hard!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.48,0:23:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Human-faced dog or no, Kanade's still Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.53,0:23:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I could spend my whole life with dog-Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.56,0:23:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be my dog, and we'd\Nlive together happily ever after!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.64,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade could never be happy\Nliving with the likes of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.33,0:23:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'd choose to live as {\i1}my{\i0} dog.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.48,0:23:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack! Not so hard! Not so... {\i1}much{\i0}!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kanade is {\i1}my{\i0} dog!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be a family dog with me!\NA {\i1}big{\i0}-family dog!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.33,0:23:40.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My{\i0} dog.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:41.61,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be happier as {\i1}my{\i0} dog!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.85,0:23:50.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,My dog! No, mine! He wants to be {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.85,0:23:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog! No, mine! He wants to be {\i1}mine{\i0}!
